{"id":6819,"date":"2012-09-21T12:37:44","date_gmt":"2012-09-21T16:37:44","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=6819"},"modified":"2025-05-14T11:33:40","modified_gmt":"2025-05-14T07:33:40","slug":"umar-competes-with-abu-bakr","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half of my wealth to the Prophet and he said, \u201c<strong>What have you left for your family<\/strong>?\u201d I said, \u201cThe same amount.\u201d Then, Abu Bakr came with everything he had. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>O Abu Bakr, what have you left for your family<\/strong>?\u201d Abu Bakr said, \u201cAllah and His Messenger.\u201d I said, \u201cBy Allah, I will never do better than Abu Bakr.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3675<\/p>\n<p>Grade:&nbsp;<strong><em>Sahih&nbsp;<\/em><\/strong>(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0645\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0637\u0627\u0628 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0635\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0642\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0630\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0627\